  "texts": [
    "The interactions and layout in DesignPrompt are designed to be consistently uniform, which allows designers to use semantics, colors and images across image information, canvas and different sections in the AI generation track.",
    "DesignPrompt also encourages designers to learn and appropriate different features innovatively.Comparing DesignPrompt with a realistic baseline, our structured observation study has investigated the expressive and exploratory power of multimodal input; the impacts of diverse interpretations of \"feeling in control\" on users' preferred ways of GenAI interaction; designers' perceptions of GenAI \"usefulness\" depending on their current design phases; and users' learning and appropriation with the system.DesignPrompt demonstrates how we can empower design practice with GenAI using more human-centered design approaches.",
    "Apart from DesignPrompt system, our research also identified empirical design implications for future research directions.Figure 2:2Figure 2: Interactions with DesignPrompt.",
    "Top: Drag image from search to canvas (a), click to open meta-data display (b), and drag elements from canvas to AI toolbar (c).",
    "Middle: AI toolbar maps multimodal input to final prompt (d) in real-time."
  ],
